  `| Pr[Game1.run(false) @ &m: res]
   - Pr[Game1.run(true) @ &m: res] |
  = `| Pr[DEM_PAS_Exp(E_s, B_s(E_kem, A)).run(false) @ &m: res]
     - Pr[DEM_PAS_Exp(E_s, B_s(E_kem, A)).run(true) @ &m: res] |.
